#: model:ir.model.fields,help:payment_stripe.field_payment_provider__stripe_webhook_secret
msgid ""
"If a webhook is enabled on your Stripe account, this signing secret must be "
"set to authenticate the messages sent from Stripe to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ຖ້າເປີດໃຊ້ Webhook ໃນບັນຊີ Stripe ຂອງທ່ານ, ຕ້ອງຕັ້ງຄ່າ Signing Secret ນີ້ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນຕົວຕົນຂອງຂໍ້ຄ"
"ວາມທີ່ສົ່ງຈາກ Stripe ຫາ Odoo."

